656
00:43:43.810 --> 00:43:45.545
Hey. listen. you're gonna
want to come home.

657
00:43:45.645 --> 00:43:48.681
Well. I'm already
on the road. Why?

658
00:43:48.748 --> 00:43:51.183
<i>Just be safe and get home
as quick as you can.</i>

659
00:43:51.283 --> 00:43:53.119
