660
00:43:53.886 --> 00:43:55.187
Is Carter?

661
00:43:55.287 --> 00:43:57.023
Yeah. we're both fine.

662
00:43:57.123 --> 00:43:59.158
Please don't lie to me.

663
00:43:59.225 --> 00:44:01.528
I never have. honey.
and I never will.

664
00:44:01.628 --> 00:44:03.830
Be back as soon as I can.

